column2: SELECT       gi.specObjID, gi.ra as gi_ra, gi.dec as gi_dec, gi.z as gi_z, gi.z_err as gi_zerr, gi.z_warning as gi_zwarning, s.z as s_z, s.zErr as s_zerr, s.zWarning as s_zwarning,   gi.spectrotype as gi_spectrotype, gi.subclass as gi_subclass, s.class as s_class, s.subClass as s_subclass, gi.reliable as gi_reliable,   ge.bptclass into mydb.MyTable_# from galSpecInfo AS gi     LEFT JOIN galSpecExtra AS ge ON gi.specObjID = ge.specObjID     LEFT JOIN specObj as s ON gi.specObjID = s.specObjID
